---
const { script = "docker run -d --name redis -p 6379:6379 redis:7-alpine\ndocker exec -it redis redis-cli" } = Astro.props;
---
<aside class="rr">
  <p class="rr__label">🎁 Run Redis in Docker first</p>
  <p class="rr__hint">Start a local Redis, then open its CLI:</p>
  <pre class="rr__code"><code>{script}</code></pre>
  <p class="rr__note">Leave this CLI open and paste each lesson's commands into it. (No Docker? Install <a href="https://redis.io/docs/latest/operate/oss_and_stack/install/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Redis</a> locally.)</p>
</aside>
